---
import Layout from "../layout/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <section class="bg-slate-800 w-full py-8">
        <section class="container w-1/2 m-auto mt-8">
            <h1 class="font-mono text-5xl text-slate-200 font-bold">
                About my
            </h1>

            <hr class="border border-b-2 border-pink-500 my-4 shadow-lg" />

            <p class="font-mono text-lg text-slate-200">
                Software engineer with more than 5 years of experience
                developing web and desktop applications. Skilled in technologies
                like C#, Javascript, and SQL with knowledge in Clouds like Azure
                and AWS. I stand out by my responsibility, compliance, and
                skills to work in a team. I am committed to innovation and
                continuously improving.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="container w-1/2 m-auto mt-8">
            <h1 class="font-mono text-4xl text-slate-200 font-bold">
                Expirience
            </h1>

            <hr class="border border-b-2 border-pink-500 my-4 shadow-lg" />

            <p class="font-mono text-lg text-slate-200 ">
                I have dedicated myself to software development since 2018, During that time, I have had the opportunity to work in companies like:
            </p>
            
            <aside class="mt-8 ml-10">
                <span class="font-mono text-2xl text-slate-200 "> 👔 Gran Colombia Gold, today Aris-Mining </span>
                <br>
                <span class="font-mono text-lg text-slate-400">March 18 of 2019 — November 12 of 2021</span>
            </aside>

            <aside class="mt-8 ml-10">
                <span class="font-mono text-2xl text-slate-200 "> 👨🏼‍💻 Pragma </span>
                <br>
                <span class="font-mono text-lg text-slate-400">November 12 of 2021 — March 23 of 2022</span>
            </aside>

            <aside class="mt-8 ml-10">
                <span class="font-mono text-2xl text-slate-200 "> 💻 SoftwareOne, Intergrupo </span>
                <br>
                <span class="font-mono text-lg text-slate-400">March 28 de 2022 — Present</span>
            </aside>
        </section>
    </section>
</Layout>
